ALGOR FROST GIANT

Algor Frost Giants are towering supernatural humanoids native to the frozen
wastelands of the northern territories.  They are OCC eligible, making them
one of the few giant races that can receive professional military or magical
training.  Their sheer physical capability makes them devastating in combat.

ATTRIBUTES (approximate ranges):
  IQ: 3-18   ME: 4-19   MA: 2-12   PS: 14-34 (Supernatural)
  PP: 3-18   PE: 10-30  PB: 2-12   Spd: 7-22

DAMAGE POOL:
  SDC: 4d6 x10 (approx 40-240)

SPECIAL ABILITIES:
  - Supernatural Physical Strength and Endurance
  - Giant size: massive reach and damage in melee
  - Natural resistance to cold environments

PENALTIES:
  - Giant size: cannot use standard equipment; conspicuous everywhere
  - Must consume vast quantities of food
  - D-Bee status in Coalition territory

OCC ELIGIBLE: Yes.
ALIGNMENT: Any.

